  "texts": [
    "In Fig. 4, the top 3 most populated labels for the DSD dataset are \"Agitation\", \"Feeling of Worthlessness\", and \"Low Mood\".",
    "However, for the D2S dataset, \"Suicidal Thought\" is the most populated label followed by \"Feelings of Worthlessness\" and \"Low Mood\", just like DSD.",
    "We use the D2S dataset because D2S crawled tweets from self-reported depressed users' timeline.",
    "Although they did not confirm whether these users have also disclosed their depression diagnosis, they mention that they analyze their profile to ensure that these users are going through depression.",
    "Since their annotation process is not as rigorous as ours, i.e., they did not develop an annotation guideline as described in the earlier section and their dataset may not contain all self-disclosed depressed users, we had to further filter those tweets before we could use them."
  ],
  "correct_citations": []
